"author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 25, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Hujr ibn Qays reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, offered a marriage proposal to Fatimah, daughter of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cShe is yours, if you treat her with the best company.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 3490 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23979,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/11\/02\/treat-women-best-way\/","url_meta":{"origin":43938,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Women: Best men treat women in best manner","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of you are the best to their women.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1978 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064d\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u062e\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064f\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43824,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/06\/29\/concise-ayah-halal-haraam\/","url_meta":{"origin":43938,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Justice: Most concise verse on Halal and Haram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Duha\u2019 reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no verse in the Quran more comprehensive for the lawful and the unlawful, the commanding and the forbidding, than this verse: Verily, Allah commands justice, grace, as well as generosity to close relatives. He forbids\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/43938","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=43938"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/43938\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=43938"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/